'''Battle Platforms''' were military-grade vehicles used by the [[Second Imperium]] in [[23 ABY/Legends|23 ABY]] that could be used as both landing craft and aerial assault vehicles. It resembled a large, flattened [[Sail barge/Legends|sail barge]] with rounded corners. A battle platform had two levels with an upper [[Bridge (starship)/Legends|command deck]] that would open automatically when they reached the atmosphere. During the [[Third Battle of Yavin]], [[Nightsisters/Legends|Nightsister]] [[Tamith Kai]] rode one of these into battle.

